NHL Player Stats

nhl_player_stats.Rd

Returns player stats for a given player ID

nhl_player_stats(player_id)

Arguments

player_id

Player unique ID

Value

Returns a named list of data frames: player, stats

Examples

  nhl_player_stats(player_id=8476899)
